生会男主席徽章和魁地奇奖杯，渴望亲情的邓布利多则看到了一双羊毛袜…那么，童年时代的三国人物又会看到什么呢？开启你的脑洞畅想一番吧！ 本次活动的规则十分简单： 体验包开启后，你可以选择最多不超过10位三国人物（性别、国别不限，人设可走正史或《三国演义》小说），你将带着他们在年满10周岁的午夜，进入霍格沃茨的有求必应室，站在神奇的厄里斯魔镜前，照见他们内心最热切的渴望。 活动过程中请务必遵守秩序，严禁一切打架斗殴或损坏物品的行为，否则一律视为任务失败，你邀请来的三国人物无论是否已经照到镜子，都将被立刻遣返，你需留在霍格沃茨奖品陈列室擦三天银器。 最后，祝大家童心永驻，长命百岁！ 更多精彩敬请移步：西斯特艾伦：西公公的活动场沙龙集锦——三国人物主题派对（长期更新）"},"attached_info":"Cj4IqJeS5vf409g9EAMaCDY0Nzg4NjY2IJTTsYUGMAA4KkAecgk0NjEyOTEyNzZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"64 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"31_1622067219.39236","card_id":"Q_451957104","target":{"id":451957104,"title":"放下喜欢了很久的人是什么感受？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/451957104","type":"question","created":1617035433,"answer_count":650,"follower_count":757,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[123902,181694,195983],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IqJeS5vf409g9EAMaCDYyNzE0MjMwIKmBiIMGMAA49QVAH3IJNDUxOTU3MTA0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"63 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"32_1622067219.3926048","card_id":"Q_456632067","target":{"id":456632067,"title":"经常找不到努力的动力，人为什么要努力？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/456632067","type":"question","created":1619412389,"answer_count":476,"follower_count":554,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[307,1761,2566,5993,6551],"comment_count":3,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"经常找不到努力的动力，努力的意义是什么，是什么支撑你努力的？"},"attached_info":"Cj8IqJeS5vf409g9EAMaCDYzNzUzODEzIKWLmYQGMAM4qgRAIHIJNDU2NjMyMDY3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"61 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"ty